name: .FMV File Extension
summary: Learn about .FMV files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: GIS data file used by the Universal Viewer program included with the FME Desktop application suite; stores settings for importing and converting spatial data; used for saving the "viewspace" of a collection of datasets.

content: NOTE: FME Desktop is a GIS data manipulation and visualization program. Since the software can manipulate many kinds of data formats, is called an ETL program, which stands for "Extract, Transform, Load."
